OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FThe previous Chief Minister will again
OL,7,Ftake Jersey's top political position
OL,8,Fafter he was re-elected without a vote
OL,9,Finto the same role.
OL,11,FSenator Lyndon Farnham was elected as
OL,12,Fthe Chief Minister Designate in
OL,13,FJersey's States Assembly today (Friday
OL,14,F19 June) after running unopposed.
OL,16,FIt was thought that Dr Helen Miles
OL,17,Fmight have challenged Lyndon Farnham
OL,18,Fafter she topped the Senatorial poll.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
