CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FHowever, in a joint statement on
OL,7,FThursday 11 June, Senator Miles backed
OL,8,FSenator Farnham as her pick for Chief
OL,9,FMinister.
OL,11,FIn his swearing-in speech today,
OL,12,FSenator Lyndon Farnham said he would
OL,13,Ftake an approach "with humility, a
OL,14,Fdeep sense of responsibility, and
OL,15,Fabove all, optimism about Jersey's
OL,16,Ffuture".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
