OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FHowever, with a council of Ministers
OL,7,Fstill to be decided next week, the
OL,8,FChief Minister Designate was hesitant
OL,9,Fto give clear-cut solutions to the
OL,10,Fmany challenges Jersey faces over the
OL,11,Fnext four years, as he also faced
OL,12,Ftough questions from the new Assembly.
OL,14,FLooking ahead to the future, the Chief
OL,15,FMinister Designate outlined five key
OL,16,Fpriorities to deal with the challenges
OL,17,Fahead:
OL,19,F1. Maintaining strong and sustainable
OL,20,Fpublic finance
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FSenator Farnham believes that
OL,7,Fimproving public finances would allow
OL,8,Fthe government to more easily invest
OL,9,Fin the island's healthcare, education,
OL,10,Fhousing, and infrastructure.
OL,12,F"Strong public finances are not simply
OL,13,Fan accounting exercise," the
OL,14,Fpolitician told the States Assembly in
OL,15,Fhis nomination speech.
OL,17,F"They provide the foundation for
OL,18,Feverything else this Assembly seeks to
OL,19,Fdo. They give us the flexibility to
OL,20,Frespond to unforeseen challenges.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,F"Over recent years, government has
OL,7,Ffaced considerable spending pressures
OL,8,F(...) However, the next Government
OL,9,Fmust place renewed emphasis on
OL,10,Ffinancial discipline and long-term
OL,11,Fsustainability."
OL,13,F2. Economic Growth
OL,15,FSenator Farnham says that successfully
OL,16,Fgrowing the economy would create
OL,17,Fbetter opportunities and support
OL,18,Fbetter living standards.
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@Epn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
