OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FHe hopes that focus on strengthening
OL,7,Ffinancial services - as well as
OL,8,Fsupporting local, small businesses -
OL,9,Fwill "maintain competitiveness".
OL,11,FFollowing his nomination speech,
OL,12,Fseveral politicians questioned how
OL,13,Fspecifically he would lead change in
OL,14,Fthe island.
OL,16,FIn response to a question from Deputy
OL,17,FCatherine Curtis on how to achieve
OL,18,Feconomic growth, the Chief Minister
OL,19,FDesignate said that the government
OL,20,Fneeds to remove business regulations.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,F"Make life easier for business, then
OL,7,Fmake more opportunities," he told the
OL,8,FStates Assembly.
OL,10,F3. Affordability and Housing
OL,12,FThe Chief Minister Designate was frank
OL,13,Fin telling the Assembly that these
OL,14,Fwere the issues that "matter most" for
OL,15,Fislanders.
OL,17,F"Too many people feel that owning a
OL,18,Fhome remains out of reach. Too many
OL,19,Fyoung Islanders question whether they
OL,20,Fwill be able to establish their future
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,F"We must continue increasing housing
OL,7,Fsupply, accelerate the delivery of
OL,8,Fapproved developments, and support
OL,9,Finitiatives that help Islanders access
OL,10,Fhome ownership."
OL,12,FHe also confirmed during questions
OL,13,Ffrom other States Members that he
OL,14,Fwould continue to support the
OL,15,Fresidential tenancy law.
OL,17,FAgain, there were questions as to how
OL,18,Fthe top politician will be able to
OL,19,Fenact change.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
