PN,35109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FAt one point in the proceedings,
OL,7,FSenator Farnham said, "We can make
OL,8,Fprobably a bit of difference to the
OL,9,Fcost of living, but it will be
OL,10,Fchallenging."
OL,12,FDeputy Louise Doublet specifically
OL,13,Fasked Senator Farnham how he would
OL,14,Faddress child poverty, who responded
OL,15,Fthat while the government supported
OL,16,Fincreases in funding, he could not
OL,17,Fgive "detailed answers" to address the
OL,18,F"severe challenges" facing islanders.
OL,20,F4. Health and Public Services
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
