PN,35110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FWith a new hospital contract signed
OL,7,Fjust before the election and a shake-
OL,8,Fup of the island's mental health
OL,9,Fservices, it's no surprise Senator
OL,10,FFarnham would also be focusing on the
OL,11,Fhealth service.
OL,13,F"Islanders need public services that
OL,14,Fare reliable and responsive.
OL,16,F"That means improving access to
OL,17,Faffordable care, supporting frontline
OL,18,Fstaff, making better use of
OL,19,Ftechnology, and placing greater
OL,20,Femphasis on prevention and early
OL,21,Fintervention.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,F"It also means completing the new
OL,7,Fhospital at Overdale in accordance
OL,8,Fwith the agreed programme, with a
OL,9,Fclear focus on delivering the safe,
OL,10,Fmodern and efficient healthcare
OL,11,Fenvironment that Islanders, patients,
OL,12,Fstaff and future generations deserve."
OL,14,FSenator Farnham also told the State
OL,15,FAssembly that a key part of the health
OL,16,Fstrategy would be to digitise the
OL,17,Fservice.
OL,19,F5. Improving the performance of
OL,20,Fgovernment
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
