OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FA big talking point for Senator
OL,7,FFarnham today was cutting
OL,8,Finefficiencies to streamline
OL,9,Fdepartmental work.
OL,11,F"Islanders rightly expect government
OL,12,Fto be efficient, responsive and
OL,13,Ffocused on delivery," he told the
OL,14,FStates Assembly.
OL,16,FAgain, questions were raised on how
OL,17,Fthe Chief Minister Designate would
OL,18,Fachieve these changes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
