CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FFor example, St Mary Connetable David
OL,7,FJohnson asked Senator Farnham whether
OL,8,Fa public service ombudsman should be
OL,9,Festablished, as previously recommended
OL,10,Fin the States.
OL,12,FHowever, Senator Farnham was cautious
OL,13,Fin his response, saying that the
OL,14,Fgovernment "have to be mindful of the
OL,15,Fcost".
OL,17,FSenator Farnham is very much the
OL,18,F'classic' Channel Island politician.
OL,26,@nD@Zrr
