OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FHis mantra of unity, collaboration,
OL,7,Fand ensuring sound fiscal governance
OL,8,Fis one of the reasons he performed so
OL,9,Fwell in the recent election.
OL,11,FBut today, he was forced to escape his
OL,12,Fpolitical comfort zone.
OL,14,FFrom pushing forward with LGBTQ+
OL,15,Frights, tackling child poverty, and
OL,16,Fhis thoughts on environmental
OL,17,Fprotection, the Chief Minister
OL,18,FDesignate faced a full raft of
OL,19,Fquestions from the island's new set of
OL,20,Fpoliticians.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781902064
OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FAnd often with Senator Farnham, it's
OL,7,Fquite hard to get a read into what he
OL,8,Freally thinks.
OL,10,FHe spoke about cutting red tape to
OL,11,Fallow business to flourish, the ever-
OL,12,Fgrowing need to ensure government
OL,13,Flives within its means by finding
OL,14,F"inefficiencies".
OL,16,FHowever, he often was honest to say he
OL,17,Fcould not give assurances to his
OL,18,Fcolleagues.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/16
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
