OL,3,CWhat are the key priorities for
OL,4,CJersey's incumbent top politician?
OL,6,FIn some respects, that's
OL,7,Funderstandable. He doesn't have his
OL,8,Fministerial team in place yet.
OL,10,FHowever, that could be a line which,
OL,11,Fif stuck to, may frustrate many
OL,12,Fpoliticians who are keen to see detail
OL,13,Fas well as delivery, in equal measure.
OL,15,FJersey has gone to the polls, and ITV
OL,16,FChannel has broken down the key
OL,17,Felection results. Listen to Jersey
OL,18,FVotes wherever you get your podcasts
OL,19,For watch on ITVX and YouTube below:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/16
